org.w3c.dom.html

Interface HTMLIFrameElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, HTMLElement, Node

    public interface HTMLIFrameElement
extends HTMLElement
    Inline subwindows. See the IFRAME element definition in HTML 4.0.
